Omollo, a former Gor Mahia defender, is expected to travel with the team for return leg of Caf Confederations Cup play-off against Napsa Stars of ZambiaHe takes up the place of Patrick Odhiambo who left to join Kakamega Homeboyz and will be expected to work closely with Portuguese Carlos Manuel Vaz Pinto to steady the ship at the record Kenyan champions Gor Mahia have appointed Sammy "Pamzo" Omollo as assistant coach.  

Omollo, a former Gor Mahia defender, is expected to travel with the team for return leg of Caf Confederations Cup play-off against Napsa Stars of Zambia.  

He takes up the place of Patrick Odhiambo who left to join Kakamega Homeboyz and will be expected to work closely with Portuguese Carlos Manuel Vaz Pinto to steady the ship at the record Kenyan champions.  



